      "text": "……お兄ちゃんは関係ないでしょ\nそもそも、入試なんてしなくても今の学校のままで……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…What does brother have to do with this?\nEven if I don't take the entrance exam‚ I can just stay at my current school…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 345.6668478008,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
