      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_02/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_02-reidad006.m4a",
      "text": "今の学校ではダメだ。医学部の合格率が高い高校に\n進学するべきだと何度も説明したはずだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No way. I've explained this to you many times‚ you need to go to\na high school with a high acceptance rate for medical school.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 354.800059954,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ichinoseliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ichinoseliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 358.7668071106
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
