      "text": "どうしてそこまで医者にこだわるの？\nどうしてそんなに私を医者にしたいの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why are you so obsessed with me becoming a doctor?\nWhy do you want me to be a doctor so badly?",
        "id": ""
      },
