      "text": "私は医者になんかなりたくない\n私は踊りたい……私は、ダンサーになりたいの！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don't want to be a doctor!\nI want to dance… I want to be a dancer!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 385.4334839499,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ichinoseliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ichinoseliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 391.9334839499
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "怜の父",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei’s",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_02/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_02-reidad008.m4a",
      "text": "何を言っているんだ\nお前はダンスをやめたんじゃなかったのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What are you talking about?!\nDidn't you quit dancing?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 394.0333973564,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_02/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_02-rei032.m4a",
      "text": "ダンスはずっと続けてた。お父さんに秘密にしてたのは\n言ったらやめさせられると思ったから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I never stopped dancing. I kept it a secret from you\nbecause I thought you'd make me quit if you found out…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 403.3334636048,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ichinoseliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ichinoseliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 406.9001302715
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "怜の父",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei’s",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_02/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_02-reidad009.m4a",
      "text": "お前は勉強が嫌でダンスに逃げているだけだ\nそんなものは本気とは言わない！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're just running away from your studies and using dance as an escape.\nI wouldn't call that serious!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 411.9667144136,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_02/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_02-rei033.m4a",
      "text": "私は本気よ！　本気でダンスをやりたいの！\nどうして分かってくれないの！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I am serious! I want to dance‚ seriously!\nWhy can't you understand?!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 418.4667379375,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ichinoseliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ichinoseliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 420.6334046042
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "怜の父",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei’s",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_02/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_02-reidad010.m4a",
      "text": "なんてことだ……お前も、あいつと同じか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Unbelievable… You're just like him…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 420.6334046042,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "怜の父",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei’s",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_02/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_02-reidad011.m4a",
      "text": "……もういい、勝手にしろ\nお前には失望した。お前にはもう何も期待しない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Fine‚ do whatever you want.\nI'm disappointed in you. I don't have any expectations for you anymore.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 431.7666737236,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ichinoseliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ichinoseliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 438.8666992819
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_02/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_02-rei034.m4a",
      "text": "分かったわ。これからは私の好きにする\n私は絶対にプロのダンサーになるから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fine. I'll do whatever I want from now on.\nI'm definitely going to be a professional dancer!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 445.9666992819,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ichireiroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ichireiroom",
      "startTime": 450.333335431
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ichireiroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ichireiroom",
      "startTime": 450.333335431
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_02/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_02-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "大切な夢を理解してもらえなくて\n怜は我慢出来なかったんですわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You couldn't hold back when your precious dream\nwasn't understood‚ right‚ Rei?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 454.6666687643,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ichireiroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ichireiroom",
      "startTime": 457.8333354309
    },
    {
